{"title":"蚕之新咏","authors":["姚欣则"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":11,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚕之新咏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姚欣则"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你曾被嘲讽为作茧自缚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默默在炼狱中超度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把日月化为彩色经纶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装点古老的黄土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绵绵情丝从心底抽出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"系上马背伴随商贾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西出长安穿越塔克拉玛干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺出了神奇的丝绸之路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年风沙撕不断"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫漫岁月难湮没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条辉煌的古文化之河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流淌在历史深处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今依然用苍凉的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织二十世纪神话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当生命融入新的传说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你便成为神圣的嫘祖"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}